ucaresystem (4.5.0ubuntu1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Flexible configuration system
  * Smart command line option handling with shFlags
  * Copy configuration to clipboard
  * Add ability to inhibit reboot/shutdown
  * A new HiDPI icon set
  * A nicer banner
  * Nicer "gui" experience
  * A neat configuration (with a background image) with Eterm if it's available
  * lolcat integration (lol), not configurable atm
  * Test suite

